{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So you want to join them if you don't give me your gold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But we didn't give the gold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I-- I had gold, for instance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I had the buttons of my uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "You know, the buttons were made from gold coins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "My mother arranged it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They were-- they were black buttons with textile over it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But I had about 12 of these gold coins, which, of course, was all left in the-- in the disinfection room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Anyhow, so-- the conditions were terrible in this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We had no bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "For 24 hours, we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "After 24 hours, everybody got a little piece of margarine, about 50 grams, which some people couldn't eat on its own.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "You know, you're hungry, you had no food for four days, and then they give you a piece of margarine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "But I tried to eat it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I managed to get some of it down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "What happened is that the commander of the block, he got the bread portion all right, but he kept it for himself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "He-- he could sell it for some onions and other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So he didn't give us the bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "He just gave us the margarine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Well, the day after that, we got a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Then we got a soup, which was so horrible that a lot of people just refused to eat it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "But I said, eat it, because it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Like a medicine, eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Just eat it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It had some-- maybe it had some beetroot in it, as well a lot of other stuff-- some potato peel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "But it was a terrible soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I tried to eat it with great difficulty with the bread, so-- just to have some nourishment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "But lot of people said I-- I rather throw it out.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
